  {
    "speaker": "interviewee",
    "tag": "SP",
    "text": "Yeah, this was taken-- we had a cruise in the Caribbean. Everybody knows me. If they want a-- a good holiday cheap, they all say ask Steve. We had-- everybody paid 2,000-plus for this trip. We paid 839 pounds. We had 15 glorious days on the Caribbean. We stopped at the Level Islands. This is my darling wife, Julie. It's a lovely picture. And I'll always remember her just as that is-- and myself, of course. And it was a pleasure to have been married to her. It was a pleasure to have known her. And I miss her very much. And I just-- never, never, never will I forget her. A lovely lady. A lovely lady. And that's only not-- that's not only me saying that. All my friends say-- will say the same. Thank you very much.",
